headline: Prologis (PLD) Valuation in Focus Following Chief Development Officer Appointment and Renewed Expansion Strategy
summary: Prologis (PLD) has announced that Damon Austin will step into the role of Chief Development Officer starting January 2026. Austin’s appointment comes as the company sharpens its focus on international growth and ongoing development efforts. See our latest analysis for Prologis. The news around Damon Austin’s appointment comes as Prologis is already riding a wave of positive momentum.
